headline: 1 Services Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: Business services providers play a critical role for enterprises, assisting them with everything from new hardware integrations to consulting and marketing. Furthermore, the demand for their offerings is rising as more clients outsource non-core functions, a trend that has enabled the industry to return 14.9% over the past six months, almost identical to the S&P 500.
